description.html:
Speaker: Andreas Möller

Managing dependencies in a PHP project can be a nightmare, but it does not have to be. In this talk, Andreas will show you how to get your dependencies under control.

Andreas Möller is a self-employed software engineer and consultant. He owns a computer and particularly enjoys modernizing legacy applications.
